{"type":"message","id":"de9cc398","parentId":"e1601de5","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:49:08.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Inspecting machine setup**\n\nI need to take action on a machine and it seems I might use exec or check the documentation. There's a possibility I'll need the node-connect skill for setting up a Telegram group chat, but that might not be necessary. I should inspect the OpenClaw configuration and check the local documentation first, starting with the OpenClaw status. It seems like using exec to look at config files could be the internal solution I need. Let's narrate that!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0ddf31285f0ccac10169c0b83289a08191b8fe2aeb2aff5cf2\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwLg1WivxHkUmzyjv7eMz-Xy5V1LDqDXObU4ER6_CyHWMDyBhrEYm5H0P1A0XWy_DeUDJWBe_sFaqYSsTC76P0IzgKwCxl9K5-fiDU74HbBb9-QADjz_aUCL4KKh1rLKctmLf1zTBBPyAjcO69gouVD71siwZ07hAwPxPaNJ99bckSrEcmarzq1cYR8zd2rT8anOhh5cmAfmUJVlGkXBnJ3zo7G7eXhLBu3skjS56di40hl7i7J3lyVZjoTOvv3Sp5tg_ZTQx4i9n-PAP-ih2KKTzxEyDC97pkUZkY9JjW2PmkG1_5e87L5q9MTcmzw36-z7RVy1-D6sOuqAd7i2_s2EmoRrpoimrMP7nHeO-OwsYtdnA1rIa1myY7m8kQCm_hw68GOg572a9OzeAPuxBIqkeWS6g5b24vnD5viuag98FvwCQ7NAbIbtgs3ElMC2xZ0ozkeArooVGlba08A66aQ2vcSVNvRF2J78ocW1q253qnQ0EUsLHhnDd_J1BluyF4gS_2xe9mlKoDcGQnVasfcVJx9s-ut5JhuoPyRZW-5j9DMAn461g3dYQscxXi4gr6yiw1AN49b_RiIzhnwoMxXEbPJeb8ArQG6KOxsrVBfhznRfOTv4jVGKKQCCzpll2IOgmrvQ7IfZ0JGPBLqhzYNVbkdxFuARvY3EBbDXQOA1rSdGHTOrZ_UTGm0bhcUbAdnTQZ8kBF7lh4Aw7KiwYuNslTXmnRbrFtD_C07G5yus1n1Ktds-wdI2sDXWV-oKYyaBmiJLXG7Y7SSnxrr3UJteAfNG4Xke2R9taC_5m_wnn2OetWRtDz5Czs8DRlZHNZZOA8IWkTx2lWcggO396G1XwxBKVCq-URmwiK1TZ7bWw9YJmMlbdZlihcbZkKu23iPLJiHUclFHJxeX-5lcEnpAaDi6JOJxu1uXjVd7T1jLd7Of0_AbkNWlvee5AYfp0Ym5n-3nGUwN_6CXAbapcmPolgSYG3_ht4rh8ASVGYrt3mEphknw6cORdEmjiNIAghFDVcyN6U3PQVTGeNLhzvICxcB5ZoUFjHM5LVd6_S0Qnn1JHkl_U1t54A3K-Y5qDNMZxMTQvq7zwWZU5XfdjBc8aGIZgCcBETWFT3H7grBksYKcN_fL7K9-KPasDWfbrwz-GUDy8xQZWGiDE9cZ6hbRBMEkRCPWqC3XEPPP4HQpotKJFW_e7e5Ifd3I