{"type":"message","id":"a600b789","parentId":"7c77abc0","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:52:23.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating system status**\n\nI’m considering if the status might be hanging due to a gateway issue, but maybe everything's still okay. I need to give a concise update, something like, \"Configuration is done, and a restart is in progress.\" It feels like I want to make sure everything is communicated clearly without overcomplicating things. I guess keeping it simple and direct is key here! Let's make sure it’s effective for whoever needs this update.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0ddf31285f0ccac10169c0b8f3ecac8191a319f3f1d03c6892\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwLj2zyvqKPUUmSYt5Lw4zgEIJv-g0fqnOvCdP5ZnLixgd-Y8fLz89w7ea7hgaJxfN5JQY6LghDudtn6jlLkZdyvFN7zq7XvggczsNyoWUAXp2rdqYZRJLxF-T02xlJWB38v92pHiMet3D-T2Oxe8lZuxFlMln7SGAOQEEoc3XwChNImqVcAMrOh9mu67zW9iuhr-rVwJVR-qip2nTs_SJfaOypnjtL3osCVFwLXgN1kDbCUhSqn7qzrhk7rXfF-jj_-BkHvUTq0KblyvSzpcgcWqjsbCb4wr7krT2D7gHn0VhBkQ5lUd1EHDDUgt1uHUU1ZRNuG51-jzuGiupGG4L7Lb5Vyi8reAQ9QA_QRmrTk1TN2tDUIiqXYrDB8-MnZP2n7m34fdwXrOdrjo-Ma9P7zW-ahu_2VMAsjCbAG2lxTy4vZvrqet_24boCUqYshePtT1r_b8C1ckkpHyfYVlDU1D09f7R3Ogxzw9PULHnwqqEj1sWPm4EyBi3E1ByadcByNApXXCIF_2WgtK5UbuDKcwGFyLHbALEp9nQGkMV5zC10Y6ArMD0uJS3X5y3Qt1vxk58cq2jzAdIt7bx4Cv3sIkHCU3j9STVbMa4lSIF5NA-7wu8qlk8AGlhSXNgvusBFWOyYnksvevVVHssBcGnGIhV4L-Jz-qQuRu4BNyzx5tdDYBAs9bUSWTeEFh7uA3ufZk3ZvQxwfKDYrrzvKutoHUNr27yqHaK4CVTmhEamv5ZlpUCLTzj6dvo5rFCLUoPP2nNZjMbfCu0l2ukYrG9KDJ6K0ldIAovozavGQ28kIStLCgPTh_6Glv67dO8UMubtRDdrpGgWIbe5Z5w5ZkPocH-bKOyKqgI6mUycJsyBtqnMDCGPecSw2EOtiVU7o5cyNFQTU0f6voF7iYgekXU0x1e6ydVAUuRGwUX59rNDU9aly4ZsS7GeJopNuldGY-PDY712kRUnmXVW_pyrbnAhFBhg==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating system status**\\n\\nI’m considering if the status might be hanging due to a gateway issue, but maybe everything's still okay. I need to give a concise update, something like, \\\"Configuration is done, and a restart is in progress.\\\" It feels like I want to make sure everything is communicated clearly without overcomplicating things. I guess keeping it simple and direct is key here! Let's make sure it’s effective for whoever needs this update.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Gần xong rồi.\n\nTôi đã:\n- mở config cho Telegram group\n- cho phép chat trong group mà không cần mention trong config OpenClaw\n- đang restart gateway để áp dụng\n\nPhần tôi **không thể tự vượt qua từ máy** là phía **Telegram bot privacy/admin**:\n- nếu bot vẫn đang bật **Privacy Mode**, nó có thể vẫn không đọc hết tin trong group\n- cách chắc ăn nhất là **add bot làm admin trong group**, hoặc **tắt privacy mode** rồi remove/add lại bot\n\nAnh thử ngay giúp tôi 2 bước ngắn này:\n1. add bot vào group đó\n2. cho bot làm **admin**\n\nXong rồi nhắn tôi:\n- **“đã add admin”**\n\ntôi sẽ kiểm tra tiếp với anh.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ddf31285f0ccac10169c0b8f684008191b1bf0d7754044dff\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":166,"output":200,"cacheRead":28928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29294,"cost":{"input":0.00041500000000000006,"output":0.003,"cacheRead":0.007232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010647}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774237934084}}
