{"type":"message","id":"51f2c444","parentId":"6dbfab95","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:44:54.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering memory recall**\n\nI'm thinking about whether I need to mention memory at all since the user asked me to remember something for the future. Maybe I should do a memory search before answering about prior conversations, but I’m not sure if that’s actually necessary right now. It seems I should agree with them and mention I can save that information. I could also offer a specific format for how I'd store it.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0ddf31285f0ccac10169c1fa9f110481919cb8779451989495\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwfqic9hD1po44NotRj1kNk0e4lBvu5jMrsDydZtWNjtEyVdxbHXQ_IDk81pcVmurvx8Xs4QFk_HsHv7YFtm_bnitXTBTOKAv98om2g4hezi1DpFoxAgzhAeAWdthwKaO5_QAm8cAK2TQJrzwa4zBd09LFWBdAL58Jft8b505RzmB8rbwGhQ8aZ75nvFIVH2qu17n-AsAVb5x7lP0nqbDyb4cYZqYOdRF9KurOIPqYuxDutWVF8rgPrjdIdWzp159IU5R9PN_e6sTyWdscQMc7a4czUZVOPoVIoJWE24vxtRCir4-C1KQ5JkG9_Bxlw_mGM8CWc5Zu5ll2P6_5wMA1cngtmpOgpv0dLfT0O0zQye9bVlruVmulE5PQy-OM4pNpyO5RcZJ10_P0JI2cl6MVdUr2GQSYm6eHgfcdU-ozzyrckafD4abGOBMQ9qRKPWG4vbNw_iV2m5AxT829eGNWFDtrlsgFA1po0YQG-NktCUJvA2Ksa187YXdIUylm1nKC8PERGilc6lIMwQhSSrPj71S9k7RVXPlSbGheMq2u_KHB-S3-4umpDYCYNjNw9kGXtjYp0nldj_e5cocpu5cfVhcXyBeT6YQj3MClc8K5w5a1cNV39KPddQoP3x8nA2V_AIU9ExBpe0B39DVh78ADuG0Y8bugen57QKLhHXvCvJe7lyy_y0UoxMLzuPrJ-zu7PtoRaaPUoVbTcmXRtWxtadqAmcpQ3-IOmINPg40cG73DgKzltowZSQEbhWJYEiRqFqKgOJELDeJ050RtABGrrn4qRpfhxBLgXSLyGqXKoi3lMlxvAxzBKVQZPQnA8ezAOghvKNLGt3qbJ7cE4Tkfk53w0OxOlW_1cXtcqP9uvqW_ReD7E212oAQP5i2OblXUeWyRT54T_fS5UvSAs2AoqXuwsDHbTOqy49hLMywSjgWm8ETYPjSSoqlFBevkOZH-Yx4yZ1cmZhszpCHA5ZVKFjBNndOq8uhbZbCPscS5yXEsnXY7PClbhlG5G4SGkpKNdkVGlCkz9ejo-6h3FbCeTpu92TZfOFizYEQl-qc3N-vprE=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering memory recall**\\n\\nI'm thinking about whether I need to mention memory at all since the user asked me to remember something for the future. Maybe I should do a memory search before answering about prior conversations, but I’m not sure if that’s actually necessary right now. It seems I should agree with them and mention I can save that information. I could also offer a specific format for how I'd store it.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Được. Anh dạy tôi quy trình, tôi sẽ lưu lại để dùng về sau.\n\nAnh cứ gửi theo kiểu nào tiện cũng được:\n- từng bước một\n- chụp màn hình + giải thích\n- FAQ\n- lỗi thường gặp + cách xử lý\n- ví dụ khách hỏi gì thì nên trả lời sao\n\nFormat dễ nhất:\n\n- **Tên app:** …\n- **App dùng để:** …\n- **Quy trình cơ bản:**  \n  1. …  \n  2. …  \n  3. …\n- **Lỗi thường gặp:** …\n- **Cách xử lý:** …\n- **Cách trả lời khách:** …\n- **Điều không được nói:** …\n\nTôi sẽ giúp anh:\n1. sắp xếp lại cho gọn\n2. lưu thành memory/tài liệu nội bộ\n3. dùng nó để rep khách sau này\n\nAnh bắt đầu gửi bài đầu tiên đi, tôi nhận và hệ thống hóa luôn.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ddf31285f0ccac10169c1faa24c2481918b100ca366258b9d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":235,"output":247,"cacheRead":37760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38242,"cost":{"input":0.0005875,"output":0.003705,"cacheRead":0.009439999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013732499999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774320285158}}
